OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGrandad wants more         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finclusion in Down's        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsyndrome bill              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man whose granddaughter has a rare   
OL,6, genetic disorder wants a larger group  
OL,7, of vulnerable people to be included in 
OL,8, a new Down's syndrome bill.            
OL,10,FChris, from Somerset, said he welcomes 
OL,11,Fthe bill, but that four-year-old Ava is
OL,12,Fbeing "discriminated against".         
OL,14,FHe said the bill, which offers         
OL,15,Flife-long care to those with Down's    
OL,16,Fsyndrome, should be inclusive of other 
OL,17,Fsyndromes, disorders, and disabilities.
OL,19,FHe has set up a petition which has more
OL,20,Fthan 2,000 signatures.                 
